---
description: Standards for idiomatic JSX conditional rendering
globs: *.tsx
---
- prefer `Conditional` from kdg-react over ternary operators for JSX rendering
- use `Conditional` with `onTrue`/`onFalse` render functions for boolean conditions
- prefer `EntityConditional` over null checks when rendering depends on entity existence
- avoid `{condition && <Component />}` patterns - use `Conditional` instead
- avoid early return patterns for loading/error states - wrap with `Conditional`
- nest `Conditional` components for multi-branch logic instead of chained ternaries
